\subsection{How to Invoke the LAMUPHYS Style File}
%
The LAMUPHYS style file is an adaptation of the \LaTeX{} ``article''
style.
Therefore you may use all ``article'' style commands to prepare your
manuscript.
LAMUPHYS style is invoked by replacing ``article'' by ``lamuphys'' in the
first
line of your document:
\begin{flushleft}
\verb|\documentstyle{lamuphys}| \\
\verb|\begin{document}|\\
\verb|<Your contribution>|\\
\verb|\end{document}|
\end{flushleft}
